{"tid":453054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"騎士緊盯白滑熱褲台妹　大馬路上打j","createTime":"2017-10-30T23:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T23:57:27.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"20c5f8511274c14941943ac95e1d7f4d490362a4","tid":453054,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T23:57:27.000Z","msg":"太噁爛！一名網友昨天晚上在《臉書》社團「爆料公社」po出一段影片，一名機車男騎士趁著停等紅綠燈時，目光盯著停在右側的熱褲女騎士，還掏出生殖器「抖動」，之後似乎要調整觀看位置，還將機車往前挪移一點，等到綠燈起步時才「收槍」。<br />\npo文的網友直呼「真有那麼饑渴嗎？都掏出來把玩了...」，其他網友也是看傻眼，紛紛痛斥「真是變態」、「什麼人都有，看隔壁穿熱褲就受不了，真噁」、「很會利用時間」、「奈米屌喔！真有勇氣的死變態」、「我鳥小的你們全都看不見」、「覺得旁邊那個女生很危險欸」、「哪麼冷還放鳥出來」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/hot/20171031/1231963\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fhot%2F20171031%2F1231963&d=en1O0unu1ryP%2FPqfndsG5P%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=da0c4da3\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/hot/20171031/1231963</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171031/640_ccf6b25ea9a8e727aa1e03ac5278d25c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171031%2F640_ccf6b25ea9a8e727aa1e03ac5278d25c.jpg&h=0ed7d869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n條女一定勁正"}]}